{"tid":1876143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成班澳洲藉支那人係湖北屌晒鬼","createTime":"2020-02-12T08:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T11:12:53.000Z","uid":49316,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"938fefa3306e2f1cf00991278d349208b6f75ec5","tid":1876143,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"叫澳洲做支那澳洲省無錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一月中仲去 真係抵死<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://amp.abc.net.au/article/11955520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famp.abc.net.au%2Farticle%2F11955520&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=1b7f97de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amp.abc.net.au/article/11955520</a><br />\n<br />\nAustralians in Wuhan told no more evacuation flights planned out of coronavirus epicentre<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIt's been 19 days since Australian Shirley Xiang, her husband Tony Chen and their three children, Christopher, 10, Summer, 4, and Matthew 2, became trapped in an apartment in Wuhan.<br />\n<br />\nKey points:<br />\n<br />\nAccording to ABC estimates, about 13 Australian children are still in Wuhan<br />\nDFAT has said there are &quot;no plans&quot; for any more evacuations<br />\nFamilies say they are scared they will catch coronavirus<br />\nSo far they have managed to isolate themselves from the coronavirus. But now they are running out of food.<br />\n<br />\nAnd they say they are running out of hope that they will be rescued by the Australian Government.<br />\n<br />\nAustralia has evacuated more than 500 of its citizens out of Wuhan, the epicentre of the deadly outbreak, with the first cohort under quarantine on Christmas Island and the second touching down in Darwin on Sunday.<br />\n<br />\nDespite several stranded Australians registering their details with the Government, at least five families say they were not notified of the departing flights, and were left behind.<br />\n<br />\nNow, families like Ms Xiang's have been told there are no more flights on the horizon."},{"pid":"9bcd0300dab1c141fc14b893063378b18344a6ee","tid":1876143,"uid":155723,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"澳洲省敢撤人即係搞澳獨"},{"pid":"baf2950db00716bf66f777ddffe069c63f470bb0","tid":1876143,"uid":49316,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"全部last name 係 XYZ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3991c655a99bd61c0ac3bbfbe8775be1e06abca","tid":1876143,"uid":292544,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"有支那護照先係支那人再係澳洲人一樣冇得走"},{"pid":"09a12a0e7e7ae7bd857dfbc0fc3e84bc3440a1ef","tid":1876143,"uid":61655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"澳洲山火, 大雨搞到個邊都未回氣。<br />\n<br />\n你們不給國家添亂"},{"pid":"dcf0e05dff68adca7c6982edb911de3e5a7355b4","tid":1876143,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"藍絲話好人好姐點會去湖北"},{"pid":"5b8393a457b20dfecacccbfc0f218ad89eb4bd3a","tid":1876143,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"快D死, 火化"},{"pid":"4b28c269c7e7fae36dda1fccd065a373caaab411","tid":1876143,"uid":171668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkEXgK4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkEXgK4.png&h=fb78be68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84806e30db328873179201070288e2453af36b65","tid":1876143,"uid":122275,